data.description: Step into this delightful ranch-style residence with front porch! Spanning 1535 sqft, this home boasts a timeless charm accentuated by a newer(2018) roof and a crisp coat of paint. Offering three inviting bedrooms and two tastefully appointed bathrooms, it harmoniously blends comfort with functionality. The open layout fosters a seamless flow between living spaces, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. With its updated roof ensuring longevity and the fresh exterior paint enhancing curb appeal, this home stands as a testament to classic elegance and modern convenience. Welcome to a haven where every detail reflects care and attention to quality living.  The backyard is fully fenced and has the back porch is screened in for your convenience and daily relaxation.    *** Seller offers a $600 stove allowance at closing either electric or gas, and a $2000 carpet/flooring allowance with an acceptable offer***
